So then, since ive been here for 5 months n also with a total amount of 40 drawings posted, lemme introduce myself a lil before postin the first comic n my authors page :D

Im PiNKpePpER, a synaesthesia(audio-visual mainly) artist who do a lot of traditional/digital art pieces everyday :))) my name is for pePpER-isH/PiNK-stUff(yea i bite, i rly do :3) n ive got a signature color in PINK, so u can always tell if im satisfied/hopeful with the results/ideas by recognizin the certain pink in my drawings. Basically i work with genuine n i use synaesthesia skills quite often, so if u want commissions of mine, which is always open, do plz be prepared n lighten my mind with any sort of inspiration :p i’ll giv u some choices to choose

As an artist, im here for Chaz Ambrose n Ambrose Restaurant. Chaz is like literally my MUSE so that i’ll never quit drawin him. Unless theres a solid rule stops me then i’ll just leave with a pity :ddd n all the deletions(sry :DDD)




The first comic will be posted soon :)
